All Implemented Interfaces:
com.icesoft.faces.async.render.Renderable
public class RequestChatController
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.icesoft.faces.async.render.Renderable

This controller is created on each request (request-scoped bean) and retrieves from all injected beans (session-scoped) whether the chat list is not null. If so (chatList > 0) it renders for each Chat a Icefaces Popup.
